{"tid":379241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似持槍男圖書館看ISIS網頁　警趕至拉人　檢鎅刀港鐵地圖","createTime":"2017-08-29T06:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T09:33:22.000Z","uid":120119,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3093a3edad2344a067687e1afdb913fbad907b34","tid":379241,"uid":120119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"沙田圓洲角公共圖書館，早上9時許，有市民發現館內一名男子手持手槍物體，大驚報警。警方接報大為緊張，大批警員趕至搜捕，最終於3樓截獲該名男子，於其身上搜出一支仿製手槍、一把鎅刀及一些刀片，於是將他拘捕。<br />\n據了解，警方相信有人曾於圖書館的電腦瀏覽極端組織伊斯蘭國(ISIS)的網頁，並檢獲一張手繪港鐵站地圖。案件交由新界南總區重案組跟進，正追查被捕男子的身分及動機。"},{"pid":"532513ea4f7c7e369b862493cc544a519d78c8a7","tid":379241,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係香港人,洗咩用港鐵地圖"},{"pid":"05ed0fd1c09ead094a1ecfd2a83cf5eb4a2b9319","tid":379241,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係香港人,洗咩用港鐵地圖</blockquote><br />\n倒轉都識背站名啦"},{"pid":"080a5ff48fce4a1c61ccf5a55fe66ff2c1f3d7d2","tid":379241,"uid":117638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ebc2f31f611afcf6246d5d0ed7de162b2f1280","tid":379241,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"傻人發現案"},{"pid":"d15d67bb2639a7f0106479825836197e3cabfd57","tid":379241,"uid":72001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係香港人,洗咩用港鐵地圖</blockquote><br />\n倒轉都識背站名啦</blockquote><br />\n港鐵地圖 唔一定指港鐵路線圖"}]}